@startuml
title UC2 NT-1 Informal Sequence (Task 8)

actor "Actor/UI" as UI
participant Controller
participant "Manual Command" as ManualCommand
participant "Manual Template" as ManualTemplate
participant "Rule Creator" as RuleCreator
participant "Condition Parser" as ConditionParser
participant "Rule Expert" as RuleExpert
database Repository

UI -> Controller : request manual update
Controller -> ManualCommand : create/execute manual command
ManualCommand -> ManualTemplate : ask template to perform manual update
ManualTemplate -> RuleCreator : validate source\ncreate rules from submitted text
RuleCreator -> ConditionParser : parse each condition
ManualTemplate -> RuleExpert : validate and rank
ManualTemplate -> Repository : replace stored rules
ManualTemplate --> Controller : return update result
Controller --> UI : show updated rules

@enduml